(28, 'UNITED SOCCER COACHES', 'united-soccer-coaches-1', 11, NULL, '<div class=\"col-md-12 wow fadeInUp animated\" style=\"animation-duration: 1s; animation-fill-mode: both; animation-name: fadeInUp; position: relative; min-height: 1px; padding-right: 15px; padding-left: 15px; float: left; width: 1200px; color: rgb(80, 80, 80); font-family: Lato, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 250); visibility: visible;\"><h3 class=\"title text-left mb50\" style=\"font-family: Raleway, Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1; color: rgb(48, 48, 48); font-size: 20px; margin-bottom: 50px !important;\"><span class=\"light\">Ian Barker - Director of Coaching Education</span></h3></div><div class=\"col-md-12\" style=\"position: relative; min-height: 1px; padding-right: 15px; padding-left: 15px; float: left; width: 1200px; color: rgb(80, 80, 80); font-family: Lato, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 250);\"><div class=\"row\" style=\"margin-right: -15px; margin-left: -15px;\"><div class=\"col-sm-12\" style=\"position: relative; min-height: 1px; padding-right: 15px; padding-left: 15px; float: left; width: 1200px;\"><div class=\"service vertical text-left wow fadeInUp animated\" style=\"animation-duration: 1s; animation-fill-mode: both; animation-name: fadeInUp; margin-bottom: 50px; position: relative; visibility: visible;\"><h3 class=\"service-title title service wow fadeInUp greenBG animated\" style=\"font-family: Raleway, Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.4; color: rgb(39, 150, 122); margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; animation-duration: 1s; animation-fill-mode: both; animation-name: fadeInUp; position: relative; visibility: visible;\">United Soccer Coaches<span class=\"light\"></span></h3><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px;\">United Soccer Coaches is an organization of American soccer coaches founded in 1941.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px;\">It is the largest soccer coaches organization in the world, with more than 30,000 members.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px;\">It offers training courses for both beginning and experienced coaches and a wide range of award programs.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"col-md-12\" style=\"position: relative; min-height: 1px; padding-right: 15px; padding-left: 15px; float: left; width: 1200px; color: rgb(80, 80, 80); font-family: Lato, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 250);\"><div class=\"row\" style=\"margin-right: -15px; margin-left: -15px;\"><div class=\"col-sm-12\" style=\"position: relative; min-height: 1px; padding-right: 15px; padding-left: 15px; float: left; width: 1200px;\"><div class=\"service vertical text-left wow fadeInUp animated\" style=\"animation-duration: 1s; animation-fill-mode: both; animation-name: fadeInUp; margin-bottom: 50px; position: relative; visibility: visible;\"><h3 class=\"service-title title service wow fadeInUp greenBG animated\" style=\"font-family: Raleway, Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.4; color: rgb(39, 150, 122); margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; animation-duration: 1s; animation-fill-mode: both; animation-name: fadeInUp; position: relative; visibility: visible;\">The Background<span class=\"light\"></span></h3><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px;\">United Soccer Coaches provides National, Advanced National, Premier, and National Youth Diploma courses for soccer coaches.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px;\">During lockdown and travel restrictions coaches were unable to travel or attend courses.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px;\">Ian Barker, Director of Coaching Education, and his team made use of the iSportsAnalysis learning management system to provide their National, Advanced National, Premier, and National Youth Diploma courses to coaches online.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px;\">These courses were attended remotely by coaches from all over the world.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"col-md-12\" style=\"position: relative; min-height: 1px; padding-right: 15px; padding-left: 15px; float: left; width: 1200px; color: rgb(80, 80, 80); font-family: Lato, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 250);\"><div class=\"row\" style=\"margin-right: -15px; margin-left: -15px;\"><div class=\"col-sm-12\" style=\"position: relative; min-height: 1px; padding-right: 15px; padding-left: 15px; float: left; width: 1200px;\"><div class=\"service vertical text-left wow fadeInUp animated\" style=\"animation-duration: 1s; animation-fill-mode: both; animation-name: fadeInUp; margin-bottom: 50px; position: relative; visibility: visible;\"><h3 class=\"service-title title service wow fadeInUp greenBG animated\" style=\"font-family: Raleway, Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.4; color: rgb(39, 150, 122); margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; animation-duration: 1s; animation-fill-mode: both; animation-name: fadeInUp; position: relative; visibility: visible;\">The Results<span class=\"light\"></span></h3><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px;\">United Soccer Coaches were able to host their courses on iSportsAnalysis and train hundreds of coaches from all over the world without them having to travel.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px;\">As part of their training course attendees were asked to analyse different aspects of football (soccer) games.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px;\">The games were hosted on iSportsAnalysis and each course attendee was able to individually analyze games using the iSportsAnalysis Sports Performance Analysis services.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px;\">Staff coaches were able to sign into iSportsAnalysis, review and assess each course attendee’s analysis, and they were able to communicate privately online.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px;\">This process has made Sports Performance Analysis available to coaches who would otherwise have to spend thousands of dollars on software.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px;\">The ability to communicate with course attendees online has made training coaches much more efficient and effective. It has also saved United Soccer Coaches and the course attendees travel expenses etc.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"col-md-12\" style=\"position: relative; min-height: 1px; padding-right: 15px; padding-left: 15px; float: left; width: 1200px; color: rgb(80, 80, 80); font-family: Lato, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 250);\"><div class=\"row\" style=\"margin-right: -15px; margin-left: -15px;\"><div class=\"col-sm-12\" style=\"position: relative; min-height: 1px; padding-right: 15px; padding-left: 15px; float: left; width: 1200px;\"><div class=\"service vertical text-left wow fadeInUp animated\" style=\"animation-duration: 1s; animation-fill-mode: both; animation-name: fadeInUp; margin-bottom: 50px; position: relative; visibility: visible;\"><h3 class=\"service-title title service wow fadeInUp greenBG animated\" style=\"font-family: Raleway, Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.4; color: rgb(39, 150, 122); margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; animation-duration: 1s; animation-fill-mode: both; animation-name: fadeInUp; position: relative; visibility: visible;\">The Process<span class=\"light\"></span></h3><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px;\">United Soccer Coaches uploaded their course videos and course related documents (PDFs, PowerPoints etc.) to the iSportsAnalysis learning management system.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px;\">Course attendees were uploaded and assigned to their relevant courses where they had access to their course videos and documents.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px;\">Course attendees also had access to the iSportsAnalysis Sports Performance Analysis services which enabled them to analyze games that were part of their course.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px;\">Each course attendees analysis was unique to them and was only viewable by themselves and Staff Coaches.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px;\">This made the analysis private, it also made the communication between the course attendee and staff coach private.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"col-md-12\" style=\"position: relative; min-height: 1px; padding-right: 15px; padding-left: 15px; float: left; width: 1200px; color: rgb(80, 80, 80); font-family: Lato, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 250);\"><div class=\"row\" style=\"margin-right: -15px; margin-left: -15px;\"><div class=\"col-sm-12\" style=\"position: relative; min-height: 1px; padding-right: 15px; padding-left: 15px; float: left; width: 1200px;\"><div class=\"service vertical text-left wow fadeInUp animated\" style=\"animation-duration: 1s; animation-fill-mode: both; animation-name: fadeInUp; margin-bottom: 50px; position: relative; visibility: visible;\"><h3 class=\"service-title title service wow fadeInUp greenBG pb10 animated\" style=\"font-family: Raleway, Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.4; color: rgb(39, 150, 122); margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; animation-duration: 1s; animation-fill-mode: both; animation-name: fadeInUp; padding-bottom: 10px; position: relative; visibility: visible;\">The Interview<span class=\"light\"></span></h3><div style=\"padding: 658.125px 0px 0px; position: relative;\"><iframe src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/637965964?h=9f0be68692&badge=0&autopause=0&player_id=0&app_id=58479\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"autoplay; fullscreen; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen=\"\" title=\"Ian-Barker-United-Soccer-Coaches-iSportsAnalysis-Case-Study-22-10-21\" data-ready=\"true\" style=\"border-width: initial; border-style: none; position: absolute; top: 0px; left: 0px; width: 1170px; height: 658.125px;\"></iframe></div></div></div></div></div>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '\"Staff coaches were able to sign into iSportsAnalysis, review and assess each course attendee’s analysis, and they were able to communicate privately online.\"', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'iSportsAnalysis-Case-Study-United-Soccer-Coaches-Ian-Barker_1697533703.png', 'iSportsAnalysis-Case-Study-United-Soccer-Coaches-Ian-Barker_1697533703.png', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'active', '2023-10-17 04:08:26', '2023-10-17 04:11:58'),
(29, 'ST CHRISTOPHER\'S SCHOOL', 'st-christopher-s-school', 11, NULL, '<div class=\"bg-lightergray no-overflow pt70 pb30\" style=\"padding-top: 70px; padding-bottom: 30px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 250); color: rgb(80, 80, 80); font-family: Lato, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; overflow: hidden !important;\"><div class=\"container \" style=\"padding-right: 15px; padding-left: 15px; width: 1200px;\"><div class=\"row\" style=\"margin-right: -15px; margin-left: -15px;\"><div class=\"col-md-12 wow fadeInUp animated\" style=\"animation-duration: 1s; animation-fill-mode: both; animation-name: fadeInUp; position: relative; min-height: 1px; padding-right: 15px; padding-left: 15px; float: left; width: 1200px; visibility: visible;\"><h3 class=\"title text-left mb50\" style=\"font-family: Raleway, Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1; color: rgb(48, 48, 48); font-size: 20px; margin-bottom: 50px !important;\"><span class=\"light\">Ben Dickinson - PE Teacher and BTEC Sports Analysis Lecturer</span></h3></div><div class=\"col-md-12\" style=\"position: relative; min-height: 1px; padding-right: 15px; padding-left: 15px; float: left; width: 1200px;\"><div class=\"row\" style=\"margin-right: -15px; margin-left: -15px;\"><div class=\"col-sm-12\" style=\"position: relative; min-height: 1px; padding-right: 15px; padding-left: 15px; float: left; width: 1200px;\"><div class=\"service vertical text-left wow fadeInUp animated\" style=\"animation-duration: 1s; animation-fill-mode: both; animation-name: fadeInUp; margin-bottom: 50px; position: relative; visibility: visible;\"><h3 class=\"service-title title service wow fadeInUp greenBG animated\" style=\"font-family: Raleway, Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.4; color: rgb(39, 150, 122); margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; animation-duration: 1s; animation-fill-mode: both; animation-name: fadeInUp; position: relative; visibility: visible;\">St Christopher\'s School - Bahrain<span class=\"light\"></span></h3><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px;\">St Christopher\'s is a British school based in Bahrain. They educate students using British curriculums.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px;\">They strive for the highest possible standards and are continuously looking for better, smarter and more effective ways for people to learn...</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"col-md-12\" style=\"position: relative; min-height: 1px; padding-right: 15px; padding-left: 15px; float: left; width: 1200px;\"><div class=\"row\" style=\"margin-right: -15px; margin-left: -15px;\"><div class=\"col-sm-12\" style=\"position: relative; min-height: 1px; padding-right: 15px; padding-left: 15px; float: left; width: 1200px;\"><div class=\"service vertical text-left wow fadeInUp animated\" style=\"animation-duration: 1s; animation-fill-mode: both; animation-name: fadeInUp; margin-bottom: 50px; position: relative; visibility: visible;\"><h3 class=\"service-title title service wow fadeInUp greenBG animated\" style=\"font-family: Raleway, Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.4; color: rgb(39, 150, 122); margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; animation-duration: 1s; animation-fill-mode: both; animation-name: fadeInUp; position: relative; visibility: visible;\">The Background<span class=\"light\"></span></h3><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px;\">Ben is a PE (Physical Education) teacher at St Christopher\'s School.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px;\">As well as teaching PE, Ben also runs the BTEC (Business and Technology Education Council) sports program for 16+ year old students.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px;\">St Christopher\'s have introduced Sports Analysis as part of their BTEC curriculum as a way of preparing students who wanted careers in sports and sports science for further education, university, and employment.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"col-md-12\" style=\"position: relative; min-height: 1px; padding-right: 15px; padding-left: 15px; float: left; width: 1200px;\"><div class=\"row\" style=\"margin-right: -15px; margin-left: -15px;\"><div class=\"col-sm-12\" style=\"position: relative; min-height: 1px; padding-right: 15px; padding-left: 15px; float: left; width: 1200px;\"><div class=\"service vertical text-left wow fadeInUp animated\" style=\"animation-duration: 1s; animation-fill-mode: both; animation-name: fadeInUp; margin-bottom: 50px; position: relative; visibility: visible;\"><h3 class=\"service-title title service wow fadeInUp greenBG animated\" style=\"font-family: Raleway, Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.4; color: rgb(39, 150, 122); margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; animation-duration: 1s; animation-fill-mode: both; animation-name: fadeInUp; position: relative; visibility: visible;\">The Results<span class=\"light\"></span></h3><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px;\">Initially students were taught to analyze soccer games using the standard iSportsAnalysis performance indicators, and they quickly moved on to analyzing other sports such as rugby and volleyball.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px;\">Students quickly learned to use iSportsAnalysis and were tagging/coding games outside of school hours.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px;\">The students engaged with each other regarding aspects of their game analysis, and were happy to share what they had learned about the performances in the games they were analyzing.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px;\">They absolutely loved using iSportsAnalysis, it was intuitive, and there were video tutorials if they got stuck.<br>They were able to draw on their videos and use the online messaging system to communicate outside the classroom setting.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px;\">Some students changed their career paths because of their new-found love of analyzing sports; some who wanted to go into law decided to specialize is sports law!</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"col-md-12\" style=\"position: relative; min-height: 1px; padding-right: 15px; padding-left: 15px; float: left; width: 1200px;\"><div class=\"row\" style=\"margin-right: -15px; margin-left: -15px;\"><div class=\"col-sm-12\" style=\"position: relative; min-height: 1px; padding-right: 15px; padding-left: 15px; float: left; width: 1200px;\"><div class=\"service vertical text-left wow fadeInUp animated\" style=\"animation-duration: 1s; animation-fill-mode: both; animation-name: fadeInUp; margin-bottom: 50px; position: relative; visibility: visible;\"><h3 class=\"service-title title service wow fadeInUp greenBG animated\" style=\"font-family: Raleway, Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.4; color: rgb(39, 150, 122); margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; animation-duration: 1s; animation-fill-mode: both; animation-name: fadeInUp; position: relative; visibility: visible;\">The Process<span class=\"light\"></span></h3><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px;\">Videoed games were uploaded to iSportsAnalysis by Ben. The students were given permission to sign-in to their iSportsAnalysis account and access the tools they needed to analyze the performances of the teams playing.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px;\">Initially students were asked to use the default performance indicators to analyze the uploaded games, they quickly moved on to creating their own set of performance indicators for their own sports based on KPIs set by Ben.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px;\">Each student\'s analysis was unique to them and was only viewable by themselves and the teacher.<br>This made the analysis private; it also made the communication between the teacher and students private.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"col-md-12\" style=\"position: relative; min-height: 1px; padding-right: 15px; padding-left: 15px; float: left; width: 1200px;\"><div class=\"row\" style=\"margin-right: -15px; margin-left: -15px;\"><div class=\"col-sm-12\" style=\"position: relative; min-height: 1px; padding-right: 15px; padding-left: 15px; float: left; width: 1200px;\"><div class=\"videoWrapper\" style=\"position: relative; padding-bottom: 658.125px; padding-top: 25px; height: 0px;\"><video id=\"videoPlayer\" controls=\"\" controlslist=\"nodownload nopicture-in-picture noremoteplayback\" style=\"display: inline-block; vertical-align: baseline; width: 1170px; border-radius: 10px;\"></video></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"callout custom no-border\" style=\"position: relative; padding: 30px 25px; background-color: rgb(39, 150, 122); overflow: hidden; border-color: rgb(39, 150, 122); color: rgb(225, 225, 225); font-family: Lato, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: center; margin-bottom: 0px !important;\"></div>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '\"Students absolutely loved using iSportsAnalysis, they were able to draw on their videos and use the online messaging system to communicate outside the classroom setting.\"', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'st-christophers-school-bahrain-225x125_1697533780.png', 'st-christophers-school-bahrain-225x125_1697533780.png', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'active', '2023-10-17 04:09:42', '2023-10-17 04:12:14'),
(30, 'ST MARY\'S UNIVERSITY', 'st-mary-s-university', 11, NULL, '<div class=\"col-md-12 wow fadeInUp animated\" style=\"animation-duration: 1s; animation-fill-mode: both; animation-name: fadeInUp; position: relative; min-height: 1px; padding-right: 15px; padding-left: 15px; float: left; width: 1200px; color: rgb(80, 80, 80); font-family: Lato, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 250); visibility: visible;\"><h3 class=\"title text-left mb50\" style=\"font-family: Raleway, Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1; color: rgb(48, 48, 48); font-size: 20px; margin-bottom: 50px !important;\"><span class=\"light\">St Mary\'s University is one of London\'s top-performing sports institutions.</span></h3></div><div class=\"col-md-12\" style=\"position: relative; min-height: 1px; padding-right: 15px; padding-left: 15px; float: left; width: 1200px; color: rgb(80, 80, 80); font-family: Lato, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 250);\"><div class=\"row\" style=\"margin-right: -15px; margin-left: -15px;\"><div class=\"col-sm-12\" style=\"position: relative; min-height: 1px; padding-right: 15px; padding-left: 15px; float: left; width: 1200px;\"><div class=\"service vertical text-left wow fadeInUp animated\" style=\"animation-duration: 1s; animation-fill-mode: both; animation-name: fadeInUp; margin-bottom: 50px; position: relative; visibility: visible;\"><h3 class=\"service-title title service wow fadeInUp greenBG animated\" style=\"font-family: Raleway, Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.4; color: rgb(39, 150, 122); margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; animation-duration: 1s; animation-fill-mode: both; animation-name: fadeInUp; position: relative; visibility: visible;\">St Mary\'s<span class=\"light\"></span></h3><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px;\">St Mary’s has a long tradition of excellence in sport-related degrees.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px;\">Their Sport Science degree is endorsed by the British Association of Sport and Exercise Scientists (BASES) (pathway specific) and many staff are active professional members of BASES.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"col-md-12\" style=\"position: relative; min-height: 1px; padding-right: 15px; padding-left: 15px; float: left; width: 1200px; color: rgb(80, 80, 80); font-family: Lato, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 250);\"><div class=\"row\" style=\"margin-right: -15px; margin-left: -15px;\"><div class=\"col-sm-12\" style=\"position: relative; min-height: 1px; padding-right: 15px; padding-left: 15px; float: left; width: 1200px;\"><div class=\"service vertical text-left wow fadeInUp animated\" style=\"animation-duration: 1s; animation-fill-mode: both; animation-name: fadeInUp; margin-bottom: 50px; position: relative; visibility: visible;\"><h3 class=\"service-title title service wow fadeInUp greenBG animated\" style=\"font-family: Raleway, Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.4; color: rgb(39, 150, 122); margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; animation-duration: 1s; animation-fill-mode: both; animation-name: fadeInUp; position: relative; visibility: visible;\">Using iSportsAnalysis to teach Sports Performance Analysis<span class=\"light\"></span></h3><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px;\">St Mary\'s University teach Performance Analysis as part of their Sports Science degree course. iSportsAnalysis has made it possible for classrooms of students to individually \"tag\" sports matches as part of their performance analysis modules.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px;\">Students now have hands on experience uploading match videos, creating Code Windows and \"tagging\" their games.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px;\">This was previously unaffordable because of the \"per user\" license costs of other software. Now students can sign into their account at any time, on any device, and practise their performance analysis skills for their chosen sports.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"col-md-12\" style=\"position: relative; min-height: 1px; padding-right: 15px; padding-left: 15px; float: left; width: 1200px; color: rgb(80, 80, 80); font-family: Lato, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 250);\"><div class=\"row\" style=\"margin-right: -15px; margin-left: -15px;\"><div class=\"col-sm-12\" style=\"position: relative; min-height: 1px; padding-right: 15px; padding-left: 15px; float: left; width: 1200px;\"><div class=\"service vertical text-left wow fadeInUp animated\" style=\"animation-duration: 1s; animation-fill-mode: both; animation-name: fadeInUp; margin-bottom: 50px; position: relative; visibility: visible;\"><h3 class=\"service-title title service wow fadeInUp greenBG animated\" style=\"font-family: Raleway, Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.4; color: rgb(39, 150, 122); margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; animation-duration: 1s; animation-fill-mode: both; animation-name: fadeInUp; position: relative; visibility: visible;\">Anthony Lockey - Senior Lecturer in Sports Biomechanics<span class=\"light\"></span></h3><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px;\">I have nothing but positive things to say about our experience with iSportsAnalysis. The product suits our needs from both an academic and applied sense.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px;\">The customer service is outstanding; any issues (and there haven’t been many) have been acted upon without delay to a more than satisfactory conclusion. With the continuing development of the product I can see us using iSportsAnalysis for years to come.</p></div></div></div></div>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '\"I have nothing but positive things to say about our experience with iSportsAnalysis, our students now have hands on experience uploading match videos and \"tagging\" their games.\"', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'iSportsAnalysis-Case-Study-St-Marys-Univeristy-London_1697533834.png', 'iSportsAnalysis-Case-Study-St-Marys-Univeristy-London_1697533834.png', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'active', '2023-10-17 04:10:35', '2023-10-17 04:12:32'),
