you have not opted into our marketing emails, you will not receive our marketing emails, you will only receive emails regarding your account and account activities. We do not share, sell, or pass your data onto anyone other than the 3rd parties we use to fulfill the purpose agreed when you gave us your information.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(80, 80, 80); font-family: Lato, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 250); text-align: justify;\">www.iSportsAnalysis.com maintain full transparency and can be contacted at any time with regards to your data and how it is processed.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(80, 80, 80); font-family: Lato, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 250); text-align: justify;\"></p><h3 style=\"font-family: Raleway, Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1; color: rgb(48, 48, 48); margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 20px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 250);\">The data we gather can be a combination of the following:</h3><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(80, 80, 80); font-family: Lato, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 250);\"></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(80, 80, 80); font-family: Lato, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 250); text-align: justify;\">First name, last name, email address, telephone/mobile phone number, age, date of birth, biometric data (if you are using our GPS devices and system), thumbnail/photos and sports information such as the sports you are involved in, your positions in those sports, fitness test information and interests you have regarding www.iSportsAnalysis.com.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(80, 80, 80); font-family: Lato, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 250); text-align: justify;\"></p><h3 style=\"font-family: Raleway, Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-heigh